title: Potential Landing Spots for NFL & Top College QBs
itunes:title: Potential Landing Spots for NFL & Top College QBs
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys predict potential landing spots for the quarterbacks in the AFC, including some big name players (1:24). Then, the pair pick landing spots for the quarterbacks in the NFC (24:09). To wrap up the show, the duo projects where the top college quarterback prospects could end up (40:06).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
